r branch (`GO:0016709`), which does not match the EC 1.14.18.- classification requested in the issue\n+- this update brings the label, text definition, EC xref, RHEA xref, MetaCyc xref, and parentage into agreement\n+\n+Validation and process checklist:\n+- [x] PLAN: issue context reviewed and scope was clear\n+- [x] PRE-VALIDATION: focused ROBOT/SPARQL verification passed before edits\n+- [ ] RESEARCH: not needed beyond the issue-provided EC/RHEA/MetaCyc correction details\n+- [x] TERM-SEARCH: inspected GO:0102177 and related parent terms in `go-edit.obo`\n+- [x] DESIGN-PATTERNS: consulted reaction-term and design-pattern guidance; no logical definition changes were needed\n+- [x] EDITS: used `obo-checkout.pl` / `obo-checkin.pl` workflow with a term file under `terms/`\n+- [x] RELATIONSHIPS: corrected the asserted `is_a` parent to match the proper EC branch\n+- [x] SPECIALIZED-EDITS: used `/reaction` guidance\n+- [x] METADATA: retained existing metadata and added the current issue tracker link\n+- [x] AUTOMATED-VALIDATION: standard ROBOT/SPARQL checks passed after edits\n+- [x] AUTOMATED-VALIDATION: `make travis_build` passed\n+- [x] REFERENCE-VALIDATION: used the PMID already present on the term and the RHEA identifier specified by the issue\n+- [x] CHANGES-COMMITTED: committed `src/ontology/go-edit.obo` only\n+\n+Note:\n+- `make travis_build` emitted pre-existing warnings about other missing RHEA identifiers elsewhere in the ontology, but the build completed successfully and the edited term validated cleanly.\n*** End Patch"},"output":"Success. Updated the following files:\nA ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\nA PR_COMMENTS.md","metadata":{"diff":"Index: /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n===================================================================\n--- /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n+++ /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,13 @@\n+Updated GO:0102177 and committed the fix locally.\n+\n